Easily manage additional security measures

We’re continuing to keep your data secure with these important new features. Now, you can:
- Add Two-Step Verification codes from most supported providers by scanning your account’s QR code
- Approve sign-in requests from multiple Xfinity users on a single device
- Rest easier knowing your data is safer than ever – we’ve added even more built-in security
